            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間29日09:38，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>上漲124.81點（或1.24%），暫報10160.39點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+4.03%</li><li>近 1 月：+34.57%</li><li>近 3 月：+20.81%</li><li>近 6 月：+39.49%</li><li>今年以來：+41.68%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以恩智浦半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NXPI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NXPI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NXPI-US</a>)領漲。恩智浦半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NXPI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NXPI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NXPI-US</a>)上漲23.39%；安森美半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ON:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ON\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ON-US</a>)上漲6.17%；英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)上漲4.47%；超捷國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MCHP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MCHP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MCHP-US</a>)上漲3.7%；美光科技(<a data-ga-click-it