            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>威士卡(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:V:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/V\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">V-US</a>)截至台北時間29日21:38股價上漲31.29美元，報340.59美元，漲幅10.12%，成交量2,983,326（股），盤中最高價341.98美元、最低價334.02美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.46%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.09%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.22%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.18%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>威士卡(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:V:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/V\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">V-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-0.21%</li> <li>近 1 月：+4.66%</li> <li>近 3 月：-5.41%</li> <li>近 6 月：-10.84%</li> <li>今年以來：-11.81%</li></ul></section></main>",
